Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺的占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給羅克薩努的邀請信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭的晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中興奮地來到了這里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們帶路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出航之前也不知道去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等...維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 就一個人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是拿著羅克薩努的邀請信來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:43.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}羅克薩努女士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以晚餐也就只有一人份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...那這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找點別的什麼東西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒帶什麼點心來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦袋做出過指示的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的東西 全都在那裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括救急套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西全都被放在學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這成為了你那歪理邪說的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自作自受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪理邪說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想被你這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為歪理邪說 只能給你麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擁有保護弱小的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是帝國軍人的三兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 一彌 一彌...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用又滿口歪理的留學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不說 我也會起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 這是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物好像被下了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來之后 所有人都被挪到這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...這是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到剛才為止吃飯的有9人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們加進去 一共11人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在變成12人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了1個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2話 由死者的靈魂托起的遇難船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 有12個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 沒有吃飯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也混到了這里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把睡著的我們 挪到這來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那樣的啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼野兔的話 是那些孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,queen berry號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圖書館里看過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前沉掉的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,queen berry號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的靈魂不能超度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨的夜晚就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把活著的人帶進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為祭品 一起沉入海里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你那個反應...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為你在講笑話 所以笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 我是很認真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs48}發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs48}燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs48}停電？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs48}快點找開關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維...維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 在干什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈..哈哈...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀......
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以來 10年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 輪到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受野兔奔跑的不是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才是野兔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 那個門鎖著...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這扇門外面已經安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 不快點的話會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 你們也是 快點兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系的 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我后面...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有人死在了眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也像是無所謂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要用救生艇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這暴風雨的海上 要用救生艇...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這船上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變成野兔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我丟在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都警告過你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加都...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植物園的維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶一樣的維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議 不可思議...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 已經
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去了一下甲板就...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 尸體哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點驚慌失措了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莫里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蘇瓦爾王國的外務部工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉蓋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親有煤礦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是內德巴庫斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在英國做舞臺演員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好下個月的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是演殺人犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是從日本來的久城一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 她是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我在哪見過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對上了這艘船的年輕人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該好好解釋一下這所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 那是什麼意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個模型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友要碰那個模型的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你警告過他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你知道那是個機關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船正是在10年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是1914年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這地中海沉掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,queen berry號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船上載著一群被叫做野兔的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭發的顏色 眼睛的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及他們的語言都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11個來自不同國度的少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大人們的某種意圖所選中的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這艘queen berry號上過了 一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被上司派來調查這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被殺了 被他們自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個目的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孩子們...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是收尸體的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體的我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼說是自相殘殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出航船就開始進水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的怪談 就是從這來的哦 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈船 queen berry號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由死者靈魂托起的遇難船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以來 正好10年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致他們的死的那些大人們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣被聚到一起 死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？又是那種笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 又是一個笑話罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑話？我可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈可以寫邀請信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這艘船確實沉入海里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用鼻子聞聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛粉刷過的 油漆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后這個葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商標上寫的 1890年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年以前釀造的蘇瓦爾產的葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是顏色還很鮮艷 味道還不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收藏這種葡萄酒的酒窖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為1914年的夏天開始的世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被戰火燒毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個葡萄酒已經弄不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 商標..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從別的瓶子上面換下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要刻意去做那種事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顯然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想完美的復制這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那墻上的血字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水淹的休息室呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有尸體消失到哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 與其用嘴說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如讓你們能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事件重新再構成一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從船的甲板上回來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然的進入剛剛呆過的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 因為門敞開著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的房間門都關著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 久城把那個門打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里也有剛才看到的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最開始在的房間 是這里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很簡單的騙術哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后這墻上的字也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再構成事件的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到的答案 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墻紙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從事先寫好的文字上面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把被貼在上面的墻紙揭下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度 只要剛剛停電的時間 就可以辦的到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 想想的話 很簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好厲害 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漏水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去廣播室 呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和船一起沉入海底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果是queen berry號的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去廣播室 從結構上看必須要去最底層才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這艘船 為什麼要弄這麼麻煩的結構
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找樓梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是...什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 很危險的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼被你小看總是讓人很生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只...只是因為擔心你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 那個說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個好強頑固的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方居然也有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這前面找到樓梯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真溫柔呢 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 拼了命的保護這個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 男孩子總歸是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不想牽手的說...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點的話 一定還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間很緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 勒死我了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從這逃出去 背起我是個重任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重任？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是重任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拿行李輕多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子 這麼輕的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 難道 是害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論腦袋再怎麼聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加只是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很小的 很小的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本把她帶出來旅行的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擁有保護弱小的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這里好像能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這樣下去會變成野兔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不變成那樣 我們才要去廣播室的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人來救我們 有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我死之前 先把你們殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 突然間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這船上啊 藏著很多的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽屜里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地毯下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了互相殘殺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔們被獵犬挑撥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互不信任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵犬？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 誰是野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔 全都死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幸存下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙現在活到現在的話 正好就是你們這個年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道什麼是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 把你們全都殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船上 只有我能逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫里斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和維多利加沒有關系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關系？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我邀請你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為帝國軍人的三兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要維多利加活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這樣的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是野兔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔和獵犬？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞不明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不明白的是久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.22,0:24:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為了只是剛剛遇到的我 做到那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
